block.p: VELECHENKO-Jeanette. On August 10, 2000 in Flemington, NJ. Beloved wife of the late Alexander, devoted mother of Andrew M., Darlene and Darius Transky. Funeral Mass Monday, August 14, 2000 at 10 AM in St. Michael's Ukrainian Catholic Church, Hillsborough, NJ. Interment to follow in Prospect Hill Cemetery, Flemington. Friends may call at the Robert L. Ford Funeral Home, 38 Highway 31, Flemington, NJ, Sunday 2-4 PM and 7-9 PM.
